				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{Process}}\,{\mathrm{motility}} = \frac{{\sqrt {({\mathrm{Length}}_{f + 1} - {\mathrm{length}}_f)^2} }}{t},$$\end{document}Processmotility=(Lengthf+1−lengthf)2t,where f is time frame and t corresponds to the time interval between consecutive frames (1 min).
